      • addTextArea

        public static java.lang.Object addTextArea​(int row,
                                           int column,
                                           boolean editable,
                                           boolean field,
                                           java.lang.String str)
        this method creates a text field or a text area. this is in one method and not two because I didn't want to write two similar methods with similar parameters, so a boolean controlls which type is created
        Parameters:
        row - how many rows of text the text should have
        column - how many columns of text the text should have
        editable - true if this is editable, false if not editable
        field - true if a JTextField, false is JTextArea
        str - String to title the object
        Returns:
        Object to be casted to either a JTextField or JTextArea
